Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{ op }
Comment: 0,0:17:02.64,0:17:04.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Give, give!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,TS SECTION
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.99,0:00:18.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She wants to replace Iwasawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.95,0:00:20.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.39,0:00:22.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yui!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.71,0:00:24.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.39,0:00:27.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.35,0:00:28.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you been listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.32,0:00:31.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a candidate for the GirlDeMo lead vocals position.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.46,0:00:32.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.65,0:00:34.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls Dead Monster is a rock band, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.92,0:00:37.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to turn it into an idol unit or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.23,0:00:38.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I really can sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.41,0:00:41.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen and judge for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.55,0:00:45.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She looks the part, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:19.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.18,0:02:19.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.95,0:02:23.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming today!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.47,0:02:31.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this part of her performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.34,0:02:32.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this that "death metal" stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.61,0:02:34.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Crazy baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.10,0:02:35.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,G{\fnNyala}-{\fn}Gonna die...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.14,0:02:36.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, looks like it was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.16,0:02:41.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She is one hell of a tomboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.31,0:02:44.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The complete opposite of the cool beauty aura that Iwasawa had.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.09,0:02:47.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if she's fit to be the lead vocalist of Girls Dead Monster...{I think it is questionable whether she should be the Girls Dead Monster vocalist.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.82,0:02:49.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we look for someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.36,0:02:50.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.24,0:02:51.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:53.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I sang fine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.37,0:02:56.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As an Iwasawa fan, I can sing all her songs!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.31,0:02:59.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your singing had no appeal.{心に訴えるもの無かったなぁ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.27,0:03:00.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,None.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:00.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.88,0:03:01.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.37,0:03:05.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cut off a budding young flower with vague comments like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.71,0:03:07.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how seniors should behave?{それでもお前ら先輩だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.87,0:03:09.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a noisy girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.37,0:03:11.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well she has the motivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.59,0:03:12.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:14.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She has passion, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.31,0:03:16.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's just trying to be trendy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.33,0:03:18.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll leave it to the other band members to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.57,0:03:19.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:20.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.37,0:03:23.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I get to play with Hisako{\fnNyala}-{\fn}san on guitar!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.31,0:03:26.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get enough of her murderous riffs!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:28.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know what goes through her head!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:29.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.13,0:03:30.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:33.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I say something bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.45,0:03:38.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't be able to pull off any big operations during the ball game tournament with the band in this state. {バンドがこんなんじゃ球技大会で大々的な作戦は行えないわね}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.93,0:03:39.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ball game tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.97,0:03:41.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They have those here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.26,0:03:43.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. This is a normal school, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.77,0:03:45.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Will we just be spectators then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.47,0:03:47.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be participating, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.32,0:03:50.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't we disappear if we do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:52.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be participating illegally, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:53.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the plan everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.56,0:03:56.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Go and gather people to make teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.44,0:03:59.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Any team which performs worse than the regular students...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:02.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,...will be subject to a punishment more fearsome than death.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.25,0:04:05.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop ignoring me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:07.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she just desperate for action since we can't do anything right now?{何も出来ないから自棄になってないか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:10.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's part of our duties to stay in shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:10.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just a test.{日々の鍛錬も俺たちの役目！それのチャックさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:12.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.93,0:04:14.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.96,0:04:15.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:16.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.74,0:04:18.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about the team!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.26,0:04:19.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's form a team, Otonashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:21.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be bad if we lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.39,0:04:23.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yurippe is serious about this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.06,0:04:25.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have other members in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.84,0:04:27.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.67,0:04:29.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I practically live on my popularity!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.44,0:04:31.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll form the strongest team!{人望で生き抜いてきたような人間だ。最強なチームを作ってやるぜ} {Timing check}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:35.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You've already joined Takamatsu's team?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.32,0:04:36.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.31,0:04:37.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.98,0:04:39.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you wait for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.81,0:04:42.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get why you think I'd wait for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.04,0:04:45.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm sure Takamatsu's team will be better than yours anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.92,0:04:49.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts, she's really athletic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:51.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's some popularity alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:52.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No choice then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.92,0:04:56.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little unfair, but let's ask the leader{\fnNyala}-{\fn}like Matsushita.{ちっとばかし卑怯だが、リーダー格の松下五段をメンバーに誘おう}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.89,0:04:58.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he's already joined a team.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.51,0:05:01.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He'd wait for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:03.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, he's a real friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.51,0:05:05.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.27,0:05:08.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually I've already joined Takeyama's team.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:09.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.36,0:05:11.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There wasn't any reason not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.13,0:05:13.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.05,0:05:13.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.94,0:05:15.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I believed in you, of all people!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.88,0:05:21.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he said that from now on he'd give me any meat udon meal tickets he picks up. {FOTC: I think we said "meat udon" in episode 1.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.58,0:05:25.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Meat...{FOTC: If we did, this is "Meat..."}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.44,0:05:26.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just now this guy was all like,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.67,0:05:29.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"He's a real friend! So embarrassing! Haha!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.29,0:05:30.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.24,0:05:32.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.74,0:05:33.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:35.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll ask TK next.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.65,0:05:37.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, TK!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:40.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, why's he called "TK"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.70,0:05:42.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what he calls himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:44.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No one knows what his real name is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.17,0:05:45.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a complete mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:48.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I trust that guy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.46,0:05:51.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:53.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're starting to look like TK. {お前TKみたいになってるからな eh?}{FOTC: Now you're starting to look like TK.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.06,0:05:59.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I didn't catch which ball game we're playing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.30,0:06:00.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Baseball.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:03.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So we need seven more people...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:04.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way that's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.48,0:06:05.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be in need of help!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.85,0:06:10.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Miss Screaming Death Metal Vocalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.42,0:06:13.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look like I'd put on a performance like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.50,0:06:14.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You really do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:16.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.58,0:06:18.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're short on members, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.24,0:06:19.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I could be useful to your team! {FOTC: Episode preview we said "I'll be useful!"}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:20.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Useful?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.43,0:06:24.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, if she gets hit by the ball, it's a dead ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.33,0:06:25.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the other team's pitcher gets thrown out...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:27.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So we just need her to get hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.02,0:06:28.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, you're in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.29,0:06:31.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your line of reasoning just now is melting and dripping out of your nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:34.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your senior, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.71,0:06:35.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.35,0:06:39.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I meant to say, it would seem that the contents of your brain have melted and is dripping out your nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.44,0:06:41.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.98,0:06:44.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts, senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:46.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in pain too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.29,0:06:48.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But she looks like the athletic type.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:50.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Otonashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.71,0:06:54.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to even imagine this girl with a screw loose as one of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.30,0:06:55.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.92,0:07:00.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You say that, but the people you've asked so far have all refused to join.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.01,0:07:01.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right! I saw that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:04.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So let Yui{\fnNyala}-{\fn}nyan{\fnKozuka Mincho Pro B}♡{\fn} join your team!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.49,0:07:06.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Say that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.01,0:07:08.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui{\fnNyala}-{\fn}nyan! {\fnKozuka Mincho Pro B}♡{\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.40,0:07:11.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what pisses me off the most about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:11.59,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Give give give!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.59,0:07:12.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:15.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiinacchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:18.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you? Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:19.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiinacchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:21.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:23.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We were looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:25.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're good at athletics, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:26.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been tested.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.61,0:07:28.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're definitely good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.41,0:07:30.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play some baseball!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.92,0:07:31.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.58,0:07:37.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been here pondering how I lost out to that new member there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.20,0:07:39.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the Guild Descent Operation?{check what did we TL ギルド降下作戦 to before?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.46,0:07:42.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's definitely unbelievable how Otonashi was the only one of us left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.92,0:07:44.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just lucky that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.34,0:07:49.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have surpassed you in every way, at all aspects of that operation...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.83,0:07:50.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.84,0:07:54.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If there were one thing I was lacking, it would be concentration.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.38,0:07:56.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm pretty sure you're way better at that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.40,0:08:02.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even since that day, I've kept this broom balanced on my fingertip.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.64,0:08:04.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's an idiot, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.56,0:08:06.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's an idiot, but she's useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.47,0:08:07.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a good opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.91,0:08:09.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:11.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of match is it going to be with you holding that broom?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.78,0:08:13.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Baseball, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.50,0:08:16.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But have your match at the proper place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.05,0:08:17.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fight one on one here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.32,0:08:19.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.85,0:08:22.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have to balance a broom, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.51,0:08:23.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.24,0:08:26.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I will demonstrate to you how strong my concentration is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:27.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, that's decided then!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.85,0:08:29.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Our idiot count increased!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:32.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So we have four people now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.16,0:08:33.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:35.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we'll go ask that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.21,0:08:42.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody would invite him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.15,0:08:44.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a simplistic guy who'll only take orders from Yurippe.{直情的でユリッペ意外の指示には従わない}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.89,0:08:46.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So basically, he's an idiot too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.99,0:08:48.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He may be an idiot but we can use him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.98,0:08:52.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And look, nobody can swing a stick around better than him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:56.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've come at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.48,0:08:59.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to settle this once and for all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:01.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But before that we'll do a warm up! {小手調べ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.26,0:09:05.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's show everyone who has the better baseball skills between you and him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.76,0:09:06.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.88,0:09:09.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get Yurippe's attention by just being strong, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.10,0:09:13.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.98,0:09:14.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:16.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He has no idea he's being used.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.94,0:09:18.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,<sign: Study Block A Roof >
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.36,0:09:23.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty much all the Battlefront members are already on a team.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:25.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We still need another five.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:26.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.15,0:09:28.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you put that broom down?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.19,0:09:30.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like a joke even when you're talking seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.86,0:09:33.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll only happen if my concentration breaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.47,0:09:35.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this then!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.52,0:09:36.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.62,0:09:37.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.50,0:09:40.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, don't fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.42,0:09:42.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata, say somethi—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.09,0:09:44.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.41,0:09:52.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.17,0:09:53.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.56,0:09:55.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.44,0:09:58.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I got lost in my thoughts for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.80,0:10:01.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, no choice then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.35,0:10:03.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess we'll go ask the ordinary students.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.50,0:10:04.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.49,0:10:07.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have friends I can ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.66,0:10:09.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:12.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:15.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we're Yui{\fnNyala}-{\fn}nyan{\fnNyala}-{\fn}san's fans...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:17.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe groupies...{勝手に親衛隊というか}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:22.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been steadily building up a repertoire of modest street performances.{ゆいには才能に溺れることなく地道にストリートライブとか積み重ねてきていますから}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:25.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So they're all just trying to be trendy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.19,0:10:26.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they going to be useful at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.70,0:10:29.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, we still only have eight people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:30.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No choice then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.76,0:10:32.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just go with what we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.50,0:10:34.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to be guerrilla participation anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:38.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be fine if we leave out center and have right and left cover the middle ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.21,0:10:40.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure that's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.21,0:11:00.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Home run!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.14,0:11:01.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:03.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go TK!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.19,0:11:05.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a total mystery what you were doing before you died!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.23,0:11:08.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop dancing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.52,0:11:15.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Woah! He just got us a point!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.06,0:11:21.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A good start to our guerrilla operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:24.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, how might Angel be feeling about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.40,0:11:26.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.42,0:11:29.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,All of the other Battlefront teams made it through the first round!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.55,0:11:32.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get this over with then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.86,0:11:35.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.58,0:11:39.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The team that advances will be the one that beats us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.18,0:11:40.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock{\fnNyala}-{\fn}paper{\fnNyala}-{\fn}scissors for who goes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.04,0:11:43.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The number of teams just keeps on increasing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.35,0:11:46.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, we're also students here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:48.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:50.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us everything you got, losers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.62,0:11:52.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll you do if they do give us everything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.59,0:11:54.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My joints are leaving their sockets!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.34,0:11:56.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to hit a home run!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.17,0:11:58.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No one was expecting you to in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.34,0:12:01.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If we lose here, we're getting a punishment game.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.89,0:12:03.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to give it everything we got.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.73,0:12:05.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're up first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.26,0:12:06.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.42,0:12:07.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.03,0:12:08.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:09.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm second,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.71,0:12:11.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina's third,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.64,0:12:14.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and fourth is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.49,0:12:17.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't get a cleanup hit, you lose, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:18.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.89,0:12:20.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's simple enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.28,0:12:21.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,7 points higher and it's a cold game.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:24.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get it over with before Angel gets here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.45,0:12:25.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.83,0:12:27.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:29.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y{\fnNyala}-{\fn}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.91,0:12:31.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y{\fnNyala}-{\fn}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:34.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A staggering lack of unity...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.34,0:12:36.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Play ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:38.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So we're going for a cold game?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.79,0:12:41.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That means I'll have to get out there as first batter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:46.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:49.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all you've got?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.08,0:12:52.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.24,0:12:53.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's more like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:12:59.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not how you play baseball!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.30,0:12:59.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.97,0:13:00.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:06.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.06,0:13:07.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough playing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.45,0:13:09.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.46,0:13:10.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:12.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.59,0:13:18.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Home run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:20.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:24.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.68,0:13:26.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I the pitcher?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:32.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda hit a home run, so you need to hold them at 0 to stay in this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:34.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are we playing against again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.55,0:13:35.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.89,0:13:39.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.94,0:13:43.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all you've got?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.73,0:13:45.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You little...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:48.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's more like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.94,0:13:49.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.34,0:13:53.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I said stop playing by yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.57,0:13:55.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even death can't cure idiocy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:08.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.93,0:14:10.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, what an idiot.{juntouni}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.43,0:14:15.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The Hinata Team has won in the third inning by cold game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.49,0:14:19.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, the Battlefront teams are all winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.13,0:14:23.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's trying their hardest so they don't have to do a punishment game more fearsome than death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:24.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.69,0:14:29.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Those subject to Yurippe's punishment games are known to be driven to madness or personality changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.83,0:14:30.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.29,0:14:32.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what kind of punishment game is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.54,0:14:34.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never had one myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.86,0:14:36.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never given one out that ba—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.32,0:14:39.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we got her to show herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.30,0:14:42.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have any weapons, just bats and gloves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.89,0:14:46.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of peaceful resolution are you going to offer us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.21,0:14:47.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This'll be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.79,0:14:52.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your team is not registered for participation in this tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:53.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:55.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,At least we're participating, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.43,0:14:59.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the student council vice{\fnNyala}-{\fn}president, Naoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.17,0:15:01.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We have created a student council team.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.85,0:15:06.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We will remove your teams with our own team.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:10.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So your members are all in the baseball club?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.05,0:15:15.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we can win this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.18,0:15:18.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your heads clean for us, losers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.18,0:15:18.33,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: She's trying to say "keep your necks clean" = "be prepared for an ass whoopin"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:21.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's two strikes for you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:22.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Any more trash talking and you're cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.64,0:15:25.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Keeping your head clean is basic hygiene!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.58,0:15:27.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.91,0:15:43.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The Takeyama team is out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.57,0:15:46.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The Takamatsu team lost by cold game.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:49.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:51.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So we only have one team left...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.48,0:15:52.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:53.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata{\fnNyala}-{\fn}san's team.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.75,0:15:58.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we were going to win against Angel fair and square, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.51,0:16:00.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What a bunch of useless idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:03.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's our turn at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:08.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We now begin the final match of the tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.13,0:16:12.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not cute at all.{FOTC: Wrong, Hinata. She's so cute, I can't help myself.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.56,0:16:14.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,At least say something to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.18,0:16:16.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Play ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.18,0:16:21.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Home run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:23.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.87,0:16:40.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Time out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:42.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.62,0:16:45.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really hard to hold off these baseball club regulars.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:48.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And our outfield is crap, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.46,0:16:57.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I had an extra meal ticket, so I gave it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.41,0:16:58.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.99,0:17:00.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, that's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.28,0:17:02.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't forget his debts over food!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.38,0:17:05.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now our outfield and back are perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.01,0:17:05.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Give, give!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:07.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit I'm going to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.95,0:17:10.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:18.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Matsushita 5th Dan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.06,0:17:21.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is starting to feel less like a baseball team and more like an acrobatics one...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.18,0:17:26.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.05,0:17:27.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Three outs, change up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:28.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.20,0:17:30.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're changing pitchers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.46,0:17:40.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If they keep this up we'll win!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:42.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad at all, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.07,0:17:43.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fair and square!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.78,0:17:47.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Has there ever been a time when things have gone this far outside Angel's plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.45,0:17:48.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Serves you right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.24,0:17:56.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yurippe{\fnNyala}-{\fn}san, you sound like a villain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.21,0:17:59.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a chance at winning this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.26,0:18:02.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The final match, one point difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.16,0:18:06.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Two outs, runners on second and third...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.97,0:18:07.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Time out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.90,0:18:09.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.21,0:18:11.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I can hold them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:13.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we can change the pitch—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.91,0:18:17.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Hinata?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.47,0:18:25.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, it's just that this is a lot like something that happened when I was alive, a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:28.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a really important match.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.02,0:18:30.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.05,0:18:33.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,shaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.95,0:18:35.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:36.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.37,0:18:38.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:41.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.63,0:18:43.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:49.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in the baseball club, and we were aiming for Koushien.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.49,0:18:53.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was ridiculously hot, and my mouth tasted like dirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.56,0:18:56.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:02.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the finals of the regional tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.73,0:19:06.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Last inning, two outs, runners on second and third.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.89,0:19:10.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a simple fly ball to second.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.60,0:19:15.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone knew where it was going to land.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:16.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.75,0:19:21.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I catch it or miss it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.10,0:19:24.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember that moment at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:30.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if I'd caught it there's no way I'd forget, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.80,0:19:33.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I missed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:36.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have nothing to say to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.64,0:19:40.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He ruined all of our efforts over the last three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:43.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What a bad luck charm. {強烈な疫病神}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:44.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.58,0:19:47.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't even moved since we got back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.61,0:19:49.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish he'd get his act together again.{立ち直れんのかな}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.46,0:19:52.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried about him. I'll ask senpai what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.58,0:20:02.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.43,0:20:04.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.51,0:20:05.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What a bummer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.86,0:20:07.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Must be harsh for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.93,0:20:10.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What you need right now is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.25,0:20:12.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.06,0:20:14.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.64,0:20:17.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think too hard about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:19.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just try it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.73,0:20:21.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll calm your nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:26.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.38,0:20:29.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.01,0:20:34.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If we win this match...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.25,0:20:35.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.95,0:20:38.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.29,0:20:41.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.67,0:20:42.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'd disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.52,0:21:09.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Finish it, Otonashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.47,0:21:18.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.18,0:21:20.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly ball to second?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.92,0:21:24.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Same as back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.96,0:21:27.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.69,0:21:31.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I catch this, will it all be over?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.43,0:21:39.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be the best feeling...{FOTC: How'd we say it in the preview?}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.93,0:21:42.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't catch it Hinata!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.15,0:21:43.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.45,0:21:44.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.89,0:21:46.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.75,0:21:53.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You let your guard down!{隙有り！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:57.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You've put me in an inverted swastika hold one too many times, you damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:00.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Home in!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.67,0:22:02.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You little...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.74,0:22:04.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,At a time like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.32,0:22:06.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.38,0:22:07.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.84,0:22:11.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what I did wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.06,0:22:12.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.94,0:22:14.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Home in!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.19,0:22:16.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Game set!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.02,0:22:17.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.09,0:22:19.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forgive you for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.64,0:22:22.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Die! Just die!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.70,0:22:23.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You two...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.70,0:22:24.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just disappear please.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.97,0:24:18.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The test is starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.28,0:24:18.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It DID come!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.97,0:24:18.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I call for their retirement!{FOTC: Withdraw!}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.65,0:24:19.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.20,0:24:20.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The plan is almost perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.80,0:24:21.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyaa! You're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.78,0:24:22.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we fight against?{FOTC: Just what are we fighting against?}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.70,0:24:24.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that!!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.88,0:24:26.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the last song Iwasawa left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.92,0:24:24.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,About the physics test...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.58,0:24:24.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I only fall in love seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.59,0:24:23.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's comical...{FOTC: Funny...}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.72,0:24:26.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I even stole that simplest of joys...{FOTC: I even took that simplest of joys from them.}
